                         <br/><br/>
                         This is equivalent to the carbon sequestered by <strong>{Math.round(impact.treesPlantedEquiv).toLocaleString()} tree seedlings</strong> grown for 10 years, or removing <strong>{Math.round(impact.carsOffRoadEquiv)} gasoline-powered passenger vehicles</strong> from the road for one year.
                     </p>
                </Card>
            </div>
        </div>
